      "id": "PopularPost216933",
      "post_content": "When they reprinted [Shock](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Shock) I thought they were setting the stage for a [Wild Mongrel](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wild Mongrel) reprint. Instead, we got this.  \nHe's almost insane in limited, but he compares infavorably to [Beastbreaker of Bala Ged](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Beastbreaker of Bala Ged) if you think about it.",
